  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The safety of Spiriva® 2.5 µg Respimat® 60 puffs (hereinafter referred to as Spiriva®
      Respimat®) in patients with severe persistent asthma under the real-world use was not
      confirmed in clinical trials.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
